rows.label: tev040901_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Zarch about the beasts on the Prone's homeworld.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Zarch about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0001
rows.name:
We hunted beasts on Tormein. Some fed us.
Some served as friends. They helped us survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0002
rows.name:
Bond between Prone and beast runs deep.
Earth aliens cannot understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0003
rows.name:
Even family names tie to beasts!
Quokett... Wolfen... Valdileo...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0004
rows.name: Such names come from fierce beasts of our homeworld.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0005
rows.name: Now even on Mira, beasts live on in us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0008
rows.name:
True Prone live beside beasts always.
Though I have none of my own now. It is shameful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0009
rows.name:
Cavern Clan has beasts. They tame vicious Miran suids.
Use them for protection.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0010
rows.name:
Soon I will tame great suid of my own.
Then I may face Cavern Clan as equal![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0011
rows.name: This is my dream. I hope you will help me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Zarch about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0012
rows.name:
I wish to kill many Cavern clansmen.
But chieftain forbids it. So I stay hand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0013
rows.name:
I do not understand this mercy. Our kin are dead.
Butchered by Cavern Clan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0014
rows.name:
Chieftain must share hatred for them!
So why does he stop me?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0015
rows.name:
Someday, I will use Odsent to avenge my mother.
I swear it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0016
rows.name:
We hunted beasts on Tormein. Some fed us.
Some served as friends. They helped us survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0017
rows.name:
Bond between Prone and beast runs deep.
Earth aliens cannot understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0018
rows.name: When you killed Odsent, you killed half of me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0019
rows.name:
I do not hold it against you. Fault is mine.
I am one who failed Odsent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0020
rows.name:
But when you killed him, my dream shattered.
Such was our bond.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0023
rows.name:
I wanted to use him for revenge.
Revenge against scum who stole my mother...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0024
rows.name:
But now Odsent's life is also stolen.
I have no dreams. No aspirations. Nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040901_MSG0025
rows.name:
So I keep delivering cargo as Sevvy Belgazus asked.
There will be no trouble.[ST:wait ]
